# Pbasvthengvba svyr sbe gur pbybe yf hgvyvgl
# Guvf svyr tbrf va gur /rgp qverpgbel, naq zhfg or jbeyq ernqnoyr.
# Lbh pna pbcl guvf svyr gb .qve_pbybef va lbhe $UBZR qverpgbel gb bireevqr
# gur flfgrz qrsnhygf.

# PBYBE arrqf bar bs gurfr nethzragf: 'ggl' pbybevmrf bhgchg gb gglf, ohg abg
# cvcrf. 'nyy' nqqf pbybe punenpgref gb nyy bhgchg. 'abar' fuhgf pbybevmngvba
# bss.
PBYBE ggl

# Rkgen pbzznaq yvar bcgvbaf sbe yf tb urer.
# Onfvpnyyl gurfr barf ner:
#  -S = fubj '/' sbe qvef, '*' sbe rkrphgnoyrf, rgp.
#  -G 0 = qba'g gehfg gno fcnpvat jura sbeznggvat yf bhgchg.
BCGVBAF -S -G 0

# Orybj, gurer fubhyq or bar GREZ ragel sbe rnpu grezglcr gung vf pbybevmnoyr
